title: CHROME-19 Pt. I with John Jannuzzi
description:
Pre-heat the oven, put on your finest pair of socks and toss a gd mf plate, boys! Throwing Fits is in the kitchen cooking up that work with Jannuzzi’s Cookies namesake master baker and recently published author of the new book ‘How to Wear Socks’, John Jannuzzi. John and the boys are straight baking this week, with piping hot takes on wedding wardrobe malfunctions, cutting a rug, post-shoe existence, beefy leg pics, being too old for TikTok, getting roasted by your grandma, getting sonned by André Leon Talley, 3 Stripe Life, sanity walks, Final Fantasy VII, The Row and much more on this very buff, but tender episode of The Only Podcast That Matters™.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
